data.description: Welcome to Saratoga Bay! Bring all qualified offers on this beautiful DiVosta Built concrete home which features a newer eat in kitchen,renovated bathrooms. Roof ,AC,and HW Heater all replaced in 2019! Gleaming newly refinished marble floors,custom built in shelving and soaring ceilings in the huge open living room! The resort style backyard features a large ,fully screened, in ground pool,a gorgeous outdoor bar,and an open rear lanai overlooking the waterfront canal! Very quiet location,yet conveniently located to I-95,Florida Turnpike and PBIA/ Palm Beach International Airport. The Ballpark of the Palm Beaches,the spring training home of the Houston Astros and Washington Nationals is nearby. Memberships  available but not mandatory for Bear Lakes CC,Golf,Tennis,Pools,Bar,Dining and more
